casebody.data:
JAMES RICHARD DUPREE v. GARY MASTERS ET AL. (14788)

Dupont, C. J., and Foti and Heiman, Js.

Submitted on briefs November 6 decision released November 28, 1995 Guy L. DePaul filed a brief for the appellant (plaintiff). Richard Blumenthal, attorney general, and LisaGut-tenberg Weiss, William J. McCullough and Michael Belzer, assistant attorneys general, filed a brief for the appellee (defendant). PER CURIAM.

The decision of the compensation review board is affirmed.
